  (5, 'Sweety, orangy, some gingery warmth... all wel balanced. The side off the bottle reads the producers rating ''extreme''... this is true for their trinidad scorpion, but not for this sauce. A heatrating of 6-7 is correct.', 'Stinus R.', NULL, true, '2024-07-29 18:24:20'),
  (4, 'Don''t get fooled by the 3 flames out of 5 on the bottle, it''s a mild sauce. A bit sweet, a bit chunky, a bit smoky... take a walk on the lighter side of life', 'Stinus R.', '8191bea5-5309-4f65-9fde-efe3ee782dd7', true, '2024-07-29 18:24:20'),
  (5, 'A lot of depth in flavour due to earthy cocoa and some heavy smoke and heat.', 'Stinus R.', '88734f6b-ff5b-4c8f-9f89-385b063a6df3', true, '2024-07-29 18:24:20'),
  (5, 'Appropriate name for this sauce. Nothing exotic, wild or crazy, it''s a more classic style hot sauce, but very well made. Not too hot so everyone can enjoy it.', 'Stinus R.', NULL, true, '2024-07-29 18:24:20'),
  (5, 'I love to have an extra spare bottle stocked. And whenever I risk of running out i just have to place a new order!', 'Stinus R.', '58678952-a869-4066-85aa-6919c770e914', true, '2024-07-29 18:24:20'),
  (5, 'I like to experiment, have some variation and try new sauces... this one keeps comming back almost every order.', 'Stinus R.', '94a91b8f-2dd1-42dc-8acc-2c986f24f1f6', true, '2024-07-29 18:24:20'),
  (5, 'Great service, as always!', 'Stinus R.', NULL, true, '2024-07-29 18:24:20'),
  (5, 'Goed in balans lekker bij bijvoorbeeld kipsnacks.', 'Sander Burger', 'c0b94fa6-f4e7-4ed6-b543-e0531797fa1c', true, '2024-06-21 18:07:07'),
