  (4, 'Delicious! Honestly I bought it because I liked the label but it was so worth it. Deep garlic flavour that brings a bit of complexity to food that are otherwise bland. Super handy if you have Dutch relatives! Go like Beyonce and keep it in your bag.', 'Matty', 'e306015a-a5b3-4db4-8a17-4e752f6439ac', true, '2024-05-20 16:36:51'),
  (5, 'Second time I''ve bought this and it''s a staple in my house now. Tart, hot and delicious. I could drink it!', 'Matty', '156523cc-ea33-4cd3-848c-7e1c9ce28dea', true, '2024-05-20 16:36:51'),
  (5, 'So delicious! Rich and deep taste, not super hot but really brings more depth to mexican cooking. A total fave', 'Matty', '88734f6b-ff5b-4c8f-9f89-385b063a6df3', true, '2024-05-20 16:36:51'),
