  (5, 'I learned about this producer at a vegan fair in Germany. I was intrigued by his friendly way and tasted some sauces. The olive oil and garlic taste impressed me most - I ordered several bottles. The delivery was speedy and uncomplicated.', 'Peter Welslau', NULL, true, '2023-01-30 14:23:01'),
